21:40.258 --> 21:42.374
We'll find some stuff. Here, stake.

21:43.386 --> 21:45.718
VINCE: Go ahead.
-We gotta get out of here now.

21:45.889 --> 21:47.004
[CHATTERING]

21:47.432 --> 21:49.172
I know, I know, but what about Rocky?

21:49.392 --> 21:51.849
-There's no time.
-He's gonna get himself in trouble.

21:52.061 --> 21:55.349
Trust me. He's gonna be in a lot more trouble
if we don't move.

22:06.743 --> 22:08.734
[WOMEN WHIMPERING]

22:17.754 --> 22:19.415
MAN:
No.

22:20.006 --> 22:21.997
No. No, no, no.

22:22.217 --> 22:24.583
Please, please, please.

22:25.011 --> 22:27.878
[MAN WHIMPERING
THEN ARLENE GASPS]

22:28.348 --> 22:29.588
GO.

22:29.807 --> 22:31.638
Miss Harris.

22:31.851 --> 22:34.308
-It's Arlene Fowler.
-And Holly Cleary.

22:34.521 --> 22:37.638
