22:48.535 --> 22:51.242
|-- Look, I mean this
in the nicest possible way...

22:52.580 --> 22:55.367
-...but aren't you gonna die anyway?
-Arlene.

22:57.502 --> 22:58.958
She's right.

22:59.921 --> 23:03.413
