29:10.958 --> 29:13.370
Come on, come on, come on. Let's go!

29:15.755 --> 29:17.086
Come on, let's go.

29:19.592 --> 29:21.878
Let's start moving these out to your truck.

29:22.094 --> 29:24.130
[CROWD CLAMORING]

29:26.098 --> 29:29.682
