32:59.436 --> 33:02.303
-When do you think they were here?
ANDY: Hard to say.

33:02.523 --> 33:04.980
No way to know, unless we do a--

33:05.192 --> 33:07.308
Two and a half days ago.

33:07.528 --> 33:11.146
