33:12.992 --> 33:15.654
This was one of the last houses
they hit before Bon Temps?

33:15.870 --> 33:19.237
If Jason's pizza forensics
are to be trusted, yeah.

33:19.456 --> 33:21.947
Why would this family stay here
like sitting ducks?

33:22.168 --> 33:24.204
Gas station was cleaned out.
Safer at home...

33:24.420 --> 33:27.708
-...than out on the road on your own.
-With a child, no less.

33:27.923 --> 33:31.962
We don't got all day. Let's spread out,
see what we can find.

33:56.285 --> 33:58.492
