35:25.291 --> 35:27.703
...I knew he was a vampire right away...

35:27.918 --> 35:31.376
...with his eyes as clear
and piercing as I've ever seen."

35:36.552 --> 35:39.419
"November 3rd, 2010.

35:39.930 --> 35:41.636
I'm trying so hard...

35:41.849 --> 35:44.181
...not to run away with my heart...

35:44.393 --> 35:47.851
...but I think I'm losing that fight.

35:48.397 --> 35:51.434
Tonight, Henry took me to
Fangtasia for the first time.

35:52.026 --> 35:54.893
I should've been scared
of this new world, but I swear...

35:55.112 --> 35:56.977
...the touch of Henry's hand just...

35:57.197 --> 35:59.813
...wipes away all my fear.

36:00.409 --> 36:02.821
