in Shreveport. You know it?

36:11.837 --> 36:13.577
Fangtasia.

36:14.006 --> 36:16.418
Well, I was thinking if I went there...

36:16.633 --> 36:19.045
...I could do some sniffing around.

36:19.261 --> 36:21.047
