36:41.867 --> 36:43.403
As am I.

36:43.952 --> 36:45.328
[SOOKIE SCOFFS]

37:18.946 --> 37:20.902
"Like I said...

37:21.532 --> 37:22.988
...I can't fight it.

37:23.200 --> 37:25.065
lam his...

37:25.786 --> 37:28.027
...totally and completely."

37:30.666 --> 37:33.408
"April 27th, 2011.

37:33.627 --> 37:36.039
There was an attack at the church tonight.

37:36.255 --> 37:38.086
Everyone who was there...

37:38.298 --> 37:42.007
