as the wedding was letting out.

37:54.440 --> 37:57.523
I wish I could ask Henry why this happened...

37:57.734 --> 37:59.190
...why they'd do such a thing.

38:01.155 --> 38:03.316
There '3 so much I wanna ask him...

38:03.532 --> 38:06.444
...since this disease took him from me. "

