38:21.800 --> 38:24.337
Still no sign of Molly and Todd.

38:25.012 --> 38:28.220
I don’t want to write it
because it makes it real, but...

38:28.432 --> 38:30.343
...I think they're gone.

38:31.101 --> 38:32.841
I wonder why I wait...

38:33.061 --> 38:35.097
...why I don'tjust crush up some pills...

38:35.314 --> 38:37.305
