Well, I hate to break it to you, but...

43:27.898 --> 43:31.641
...you fell for him the same way that
every single person on the entire planet...

43:31.860 --> 43:33.270
...falls for their first love.

43:33.695 --> 43:35.560
Hard and fast.

43:35.781 --> 43:37.737
All's that makes you is...

43:38.825 --> 43:40.611
...a human.

43:42.204 --> 43:44.991
[VOICE BREAKING]
I appreciate you saying that.

43:45.207 --> 43:46.868
I do.

43:47.542 --> 43:50.955
To be honest, all I'm thinking about
right now is how...

43:51.171 --> 43:54.914
...our town is gonna end up
exactly like Saint Alice.

43:55.133 --> 43:57.340
They're coming back, Alcide.

43:57.552 --> 44:00.544
One way or another,
that's where we're headed.

44:01.515 --> 44:03.005
I could keep driving.

44:03.767 --> 44:05.382
We got a full tank of gas.

44:09.147 --> 44:10.683
We could save ourselves.

44:14.569 --> 44:16.150
No.

44:17.447 --> 44:19.824
No, that's not the answer.

44:27.415 --> 44:29.246
VAMPIRE 1:
Anybody need to feed right away?

44:29.459 --> 44:31.836
VAMPIRES: No.
VAMPIRE 2: Set the clock.

44:32.045 --> 44:33.910
Not a second past 15 minutes.

44:34.130 --> 44:35.836
I know, I know. Jesus Christ.

44:36.007 --> 44:37.998
[CLOCK BEEPING]

44:46.810 --> 44:49.426
I want to be the sleep monitor.

44:50.605 --> 44:53.187
Why? Aren't you tired?

44:53.400 --> 44:56.062
Oh, you know I am.
That's just the problem.

44:56.278 --> 44:58.314
We all know that I'm the weakest one here...

44:58.530 --> 45:01.738
...and you're waiting for me to die
so there's one less mouth to feed.

45:01.950 --> 45:04.282
-I think you're being paranoid.
-Either way...

45:04.494 --> 45:06.576
...I don't trust Ronnie to wake me.

45:06.788 --> 45:08.369
I'd rather just do the job myself.

45:08.582 --> 45:11.415
Let her do it. Just shut up.

45:15.505 --> 45:18.463
Fine. Ronnie, you can take a nap.

45:18.675 --> 45:22.259
And you can set the clock
for 14 and a half minutes.

45:24.014 --> 45:25.629
Fine with me.

45:34.024 --> 45:37.357
[CLOCK BEEPING]

45:45.285 --> 45:47.276
[ARLENE SIGHS]

45:48.038 --> 45:49.744
[DOOR OPENS]

45:49.915 --> 45:52.577
We have exactly 12 minutes
to get y'all out of here.

45:52.792 --> 45:54.407
Betty, you don't look so good.

45:54.628 --> 45:56.038
HOLLY:
Are you okay?

45:57.130 --> 46:00.714
I haven't slept and I'm gonna have to
feed on one of you before we do this.

46:01.927 --> 46:03.463
Who's it gonna be?

46:05.764 --> 46:07.220
You can have my blood.

46:07.432 --> 46:08.968
It's the least I can give you.

46:09.184 --> 46:11.345
It's gonna need to be the femoral artery.

46:11.561 --> 46:15.349
If they find us and you got bite marks,
there'll be no way to cover this up.

46:16.483 --> 46:18.769
-Okay.
-Let's make it quick.

46:28.828 --> 46:30.489
[SCREAMS]

46:34.626 --> 46:36.082
[WHISPERS]
Are you okay?

46:37.170 --> 46:39.001
[G RU NTS]

46:44.344 --> 46:48.758
Aah! Oh. Oh, Betty. Ow.

46:54.396 --> 46:55.977
Betty?

46:56.147 --> 46:57.478
[ALL SCREAMING]

47:05.949 --> 47:07.940
JESSICA:
What the hell?

47:11.538 --> 47:12.527
[DOOR BANGS]

47:12.706 --> 47:14.242
ANDY:
Adilyn?

47:15.333 --> 47:16.618
Fuck.

47:17.919 --> 47:19.284
Honey!

47:19.504 --> 47:21.335
Fuck.

47:24.009 --> 47:25.419
Sweetheart?

47:27.929 --> 47:29.794
Adilyn?

47:31.182 --> 47:32.592
Andy?

47:33.476 --> 47:35.182
In the attic.

47:39.482 --> 47:40.517
[SIGHS]

47:44.779 --> 47:47.111
-How'd you get in here?
-She's in trouble.

47:47.323 --> 47:49.154
-How'd you get in here?
-She invited me.

47:50.744 --> 47:52.905
You ate her, didn't you? You fucking eat her?

47:53.121 --> 47:54.486
You finish her this time?

47:55.790 --> 47:58.748
-Unh!
-Look around! DO you see any Sign of her...

47:58.960 --> 48:01.747
...any trace of harm that I did to her?

48:01.963 --> 48:06.332
For the last time, I am not here to hurt you.
I am here to fucking help you.

48:07.427 --> 48:09.042
Then where the hell is she?

48:09.929 --> 48:12.181
I don't know for sure, but she is in trouble.

48:12.390 --> 48:14.221
Goddamn it.

48:14.434 --> 48:16.390
Shit.

48:24.194 --> 48:26.526
When the sun sets,
I'm going to find her, Andy.

48:27.739 --> 48:29.730
And I will, I'll find her.

48:30.158 --> 48:31.523
Question is...

48:32.202 --> 48:35.365
...are you coming with me or not?

48:41.711 --> 48:44.794
I can't remember being this tired in my life.

48:46.382 --> 48:48.464
I'm gonna catch a few minutes of shut-eye.

48:48.676 --> 48:50.758
Hey, not smelling like that, you're not.

48:50.970 --> 48:53.803
Just take a shower
before you get into our sheets.

48:54.015 --> 48:56.176
-All right, fair enough.
-Hey.

49:09.948 --> 49:13.691
You know, I think you like me better
with a little extra stink.

49:14.786 --> 49:15.866
GO.

49:16.037 --> 49:17.368
[ALCIDE CHUCKLES]

49:53.032 --> 49:54.283
[KNOCKING]

49:56.411 --> 49:57.821
SooHe.

49:58.037 --> 49:59.493
Can you still sense my fear?

50:00.373 --> 50:01.658
Why are you here?

50:01.875 --> 50:04.082
If I got myself into some serious shit...

50:05.587 --> 50:07.248
...would you be able to feel me?

50:27.483 --> 50:30.475
Un-fucking-believable.

50:37.952 --> 50:38.941
WOMAN [IN FRENCH]:

50:39.162 --> 50:41.778
He won't take my blood.
I don't understand!

50:44.918 --> 50:46.909
[GASPS]

50:51.216 --> 50:53.172
ERIC:
You found me.
